{
  "sn6.9:0.1": "Saṃyutta Nikāya 6 ",
  "sn6.9:0.2": "1. Paṭhamavagga ",
  "sn6.9:0.3": "9. Turūbrahmasutta ",
  "sn6.9:1.1": "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. ",
  "sn6.9:1.2": "Tena kho pana samayena kokāliko bhikkhu ābādhiko hoti dukkhito bāḷhagilāno. ",
  "sn6.9:1.3": "Atha kho turū paccekabrahmā abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇo kevalakappaṃ jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yena kokāliko bhikkhu tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā vehāsaṃ ṭhito kokālikaṃ bhikkhuṃ etadavoca: ",
  "sn6.9:1.4": "“pasādehi, kokālika, sāriputtamoggallānesu cittaṃ. ",
  "sn6.9:1.5": "Pesalā sāriputtamoggallānā”ti. ",
  "sn6.9:1.6": "“Kosi tvaṃ, āvuso”ti? ",
  "sn6.9:1.7": "“Ahaṃ turū paccekabrahmā”ti. ",
  "sn6.9:1.8": "“Nanu tvaṃ, āvuso, bhagavatā anāgāmī byākato, atha kiñcarahi idhāgato? ",
  "sn6.9:1.9": "Passa, yāvañca te idaṃ aparaddhan”ti. ",
  "sn6.9:2.1": "“Purisassa hi jātassa, ",
  "sn6.9:2.2": "kuṭhārī jāyate mukhe; ",
  "sn6.9:2.3": "Yāya chindati attānaṃ, ",
  "sn6.9:2.4": "bālo dubbhāsitaṃ bhaṇaṃ. ",
  "sn6.9:3.1": "Yo nindiyaṃ pasaṃsati, ",
  "sn6.9:3.2": "Taṃ vā nindati yo pasaṃsiyo; ",
  "sn6.9:3.3": "Vicināti mukhena so kaliṃ, ",
  "sn6.9:3.4": "Kalinā tena sukhaṃ na vindati. ",
  "sn6.9:4.1": "Appamattako ayaṃ kali, ",
  "sn6.9:4.2": "Yo akkhesu dhanaparājayo; ",
  "sn6.9:4.3": "Sabbassāpi sahāpi attanā, ",
  "sn6.9:4.4": "Ayameva mahantataro kali; ",
  "sn6.9:4.5": "Yo sugatesu manaṃ padosaye. ",
  "sn6.9:5.1": "Sataṃ sahassānaṃ nirabbudānaṃ, ",
  "sn6.9:5.2": "Chattiṃsati pañca ca abbudāni; ",
  "sn6.9:5.3": "Yamariyagarahī nirayaṃ upeti, ",
  "sn6.9:5.4": "Vācaṃ manañca paṇidhāya pāpakan”ti. "
}